Description: The package provides access to teaching materials for various statistics courses, 
    which are stored in a GitHub repository. The default repository is 'sigbertklinke/mmstat4.data', 
    which contains R programmes, Shiny apps and PDF documents. Additionally, some functions are 
    implemented that are needed for the Shiny apps. 
